data.description: Charming home on a large corner lot in Coast Village. 3 bedrooms with 1.1 baths and convereted sunroom with its own entry. Many upgrades throughout including laminate floor, ceiling fans, newer roof, crown molding and cabinets. Vaulted ceilings in living room. Kitchen with skylight and breakfast bar. Primary with half bath. Gated corned lot with site-built tool shed with electric. Gated community, monthy dues include water, trash, sewer. A jem in the village!
